3
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:15,280
Ancestor.

4
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:18,079
I came here with a mission.

5
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,180
Guanbu Committee.

6
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:21,440
But if I go back empty-handed,

7
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,680
I'm afraid the Emperor will punish me.

8
00:02:24,480 --> 00:02:26,880
I have a family to feed.

9
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,120
How pitiful.

10
00:02:35,079 --> 00:02:36,079
So young,

11
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,880
