20
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:03,200
In ancient times, there were four great fox clans:

21
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,120
Qingqiu,

22
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:05,080
Tushan,

23
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:06,400
Yousu,

24
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:07,480
