25
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,680
Since that great demon's surname is Tu,

26
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:12,160
he must be a descendant of the Tushan clan.

27
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,160
Exactly.

28
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:17,240
Tu Luohua is precisely the patriarch of the Tushan clan.

29
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:19,370
He commands countless lesser demons,

30
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:23,120
