31
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,640
Besides Leilong and Ruixi...

32
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:26,500
Didn't we kill Leilong and Ruixi?

33
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:29,480
Besides Leilong and Ruixi,

34
00:03:29,840 --> 00:03:31,440
