54
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:24,600
You must not leave, my lord.

55
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:25,880
I will.

56
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,500
I will definitely be here.

57
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:30,920
Please do me a favor and collect my corpse when the time comes.

58
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:34,960
Then how about seeking help from the Directorate of Astronomy again?

59
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:36,560
That is naturally possible.

60
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:39,520
The Second-Grade Warlocks of the Directorate of Astronomy are all in the capital.

61
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:40,880
From the capital to here,

62
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:43,080
